Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:14.89,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(473.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:15.24,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:18.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:23.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:26.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:30.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.51,0:00:33.68,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:36.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:40.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:44.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:48.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:51.07,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:54.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:59.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:02.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:11.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.06,0:01:13.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:15.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.34,0:01:23.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker broke a violent criminal\Non death row out of jail
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.71,0:01:25.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and doused him in\Npoison mushroom extract
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.31,0:01:26.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to create the monster\Nyou see before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:30.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kinokomorg is a formidable\Ncyborg who breathes out spores
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.25,0:01:33.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,that puts humans in a state\Nof suspended animation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.65,0:01:37.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When our Kamen Rider confronted him to\Nbravely put a stop to Shocker's scheme,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.10,0:01:39.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he too was bathed in\Nthe spores and captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:43.73,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(537.167,280.389)}Defeat Kinokomorg!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,At last,\Nwe'll be rid of the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Kinokomorg!\NCut him in two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.78,0:02:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be fun to\Nkill him like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.18,0:02:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We must restore his consciousness\Nso he'll experience the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise and shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.92,0:02:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm about to slice\Nyour body in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.91,0:02:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll take my\Ntime doing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're looking forward to\Nhearing your screams of agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, turn it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Ichimonji Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please.\NYou'd do the same for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be taking this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.28,0:04:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki. We need to get out of\Nhere, fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'm in your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The exit is that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...\Nit's a special optical barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:05:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... we can see out,\Nbut we can't pass through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was clinging to the\Nroof of their truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... they're on the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't escape us now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...\Nthere's nothing we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki. This might hurt a\Nbit, but try to bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are something, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's in this bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what they injected\Ninto you to wake you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it might be\Nuseful, so I snatched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.71,0:05:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't know until\NI run some tests,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but it looks like the\Nchlorophyll from a plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that have\Nto do with mushrooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:06:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mushrooms are a kind of plant, but they're\Na lower species with no chlorophyll,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and can't assimilate\Ncarbon dioxide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They absorb nutrients from other\Nplants and animals instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.32,0:06:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to try injecting this\Ninto the paralyzed children.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't experiment on humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But they have no hope of\Nrecovery as things stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, take the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you increase the dosage?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all I have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What will we do about\Nthe other children?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just use it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Koike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.93,0:07:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to analyze that\Nsubstance and create more of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In large amounts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We may yet see more\Nvictims like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem to be feeling\Na lot better, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But Goro's still unconscious...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't the boys\Nfound a cure yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Hiroshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak to me, Hiroshi! Hiroshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.16,0:08:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak to me, Hiroshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak to me, Hiroshi! Hiroshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimiko! Kimiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!\NWe need to call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Will she be all right, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look good...\Ntheir heart rates keep dropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there any\Nway to treat them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... you have to save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally saved\Nthem from Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not going to know\Nwhat you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.37,0:08:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you?\NWhat's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!\NShe's acting strangely, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no... it's contagious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.06,0:09:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! We can't call an\Nambulance to a hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But... still...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If I stay in that\Nhospital, I'll die...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:17.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The epidemic previously confined to the\NKanto Region is now spreading nationwide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:21.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Those who come in contact with a carrier\Nwill contract the disease within one hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:24.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The infected can be seen lying in the\Nstreets with nobody to treat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:27.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,All lines of transportation\Nwill be closed in
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:30.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,order to prevent further\Nspread of the disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato,\Nthis is really getting serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Nothing yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to cause two\Nmore chemical changes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,then add chlorophyll\Nto the extract.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:10:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:10:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to save those\Nchildren, too, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, Koike?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. This just might work...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato,\NI need your help as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Our experiment was a success, but Ichimonji\NHayato foiled our plans once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Kinokomorg!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy Ichimonji Hayato!\NDestroy the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:13:00.24,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(321,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.\NThanks for your patronage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,One of our clients sent\Nthese flowers for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please shop with us\Nagain in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Aren't they beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could have sent them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.36,0:13:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there's\Nsomething inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:24.18,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs60\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}To the Members of\Nthe Racing Club
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:26.27,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs60\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Ichimonji Hayato
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.65,0:13:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, they're from Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Congratulations on your\Nrecovery, ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you see now that Shocker\Nis a force to be feared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you lay off the tomboy antics\Nand start bridal training already?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that nasty jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's absolutely right, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not that weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.75,0:14:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NWe can beat Shocker easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!\NIt's time for some payback!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You girls just got\Nout of the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you be more\Nladylike, like Hayato says?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna eat\Nall of your cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with those girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.11,0:14:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tachibana?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, those tomboys...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They're hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Hayato off doing at\Nan important time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:14:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What a creepy place...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be a secret entrance\Nsomewhere around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that mushroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!\NIt might be poisonous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.38,0:16:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.59,0:17:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Learned your lesson\Nyet, tomboys?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiots... stay close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... we're trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.77,0:18:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinokomorg was here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never interfere\Nwith my plans ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.67,0:18:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato will be here soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, we'll witness the\Nend of Ichimonji Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Your allies will soon be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! They got us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.67,0:19:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a stubborn one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten the power\Nthat the Kamen Rider wields?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.61,0:20:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari,\Nthere's a knife on my belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.79,0:20:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.72,0:21:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.58,0:22:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.73,0:22:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.37,0:22:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, look alive, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.98,0:22:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Get home quickly, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.38,0:23:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.12,0:23:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.23,0:23:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.44,0:23:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.28,0:23:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.77,0:23:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And there he goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.14,0:23:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to thank him...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.57,0:23:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.49,0:23:24.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato,\Nthe Kamen Rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.45,0:23:26.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,defeated Kinokomorg after\Na long and difficult battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.61,0:23:30.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But this has only increased his\Nresolve to stand against the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.44,0:23:34.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,powerful monsters that\NShocker continues to send.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:40.55,Cont,,560,0,140,,{\blur.8\fad(0,480)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.87,0:23:42.85,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.87,0:23:44.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:46.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is Jigoku Thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.25,0:23:48.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The monster Jigoku Thunder creates\Nantlion pits that gum up traffic,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.84,0:23:51.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,which they plan to\Nuse to conquer Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.67,0:23:53.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Jigoku Thunder's\Ncommander, Colonel Zol,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.22,0:23:55.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,targets Kamen Rider by disguising\Nhimself as Taki Kazuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.86,0:24:00.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for more Kamen\NRider in "The Terrifying Antlion Pit."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.18,0:24:00.85,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,260.389)}The Terrifying Antlion Pit
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:10.88,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.47,0:24:13.47,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.47,0:24:15.43,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.43,0:24:18.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.98,0:24:20.85,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.85,0:24:22.73,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.73,0:24:24.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.52,0:24:25.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.32,0:24:28.36,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.40,0:24:34.07,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.07,0:24:37.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.66,0:24:41.33,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.75,0:24:45.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!